title: MisterMusic Show 356 new indie, alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 356 [2 hours] 192kbps MP3

New music all over this week's show. Tunes by Metric, Yukon Blonde, Chappo, Day Wave, Lindsey Cohen, and Paul Weller. Plus the 'Oldie of the Week' from 15 years ago. A song that remained number 1 for 6 weeks in May and June on the modern rock chart that year.

It's over 5 decades of classic hits broadcast weekly and heard all over the globe- The MisterMusic Show.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
